      "text": "ライブバトルでも調子を崩しているし\nもしかすると悩みがあるのかもしれないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She also seemed to struggle during the live battles.\nMaybe she has some worries.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.1637217794,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "月ストとの合同練習が始まったら\nさくらも琴乃を気に掛けてやってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When the joint practice with Moon Tempest starts‚\nplease keep an eye on Kotono too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.0970551127,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 98.7970551127
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました\n琴乃ちゃんが元気になれるように声を掛けてみますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Understood. I'll try talking to Kotono-chan\nto help her feel better.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.4666699569,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（さくらの太陽のような明るさが）\n（琴乃の助けになるといいが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I hope Sakura's sunny disposition）\n（helps Kotono in some way…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.2424799714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.6424799714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_noon",
      "startTime": 111.8758092357
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！\n今朝のネットニュースを見ましたか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!\nHave you seen this morning's internet news?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.5666745345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ニュース？　さくら達で麻奈の曲を歌うことが\n発表されてネットで話題になっていたが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "News? Sunny Peace announced that they will sing\nMana's song‚ and it's been a topic on the internet…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.1185084296,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8148.167567199991,
          "startTime": 129.2666759968
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "それだけじゃありません！\n記事にはこう書いてあるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not just that! The article says this:\n\"The immensely popular Sunny Peace covering",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.633340184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "「人気絶頂のサニーピースが伝説のアイドル長瀬麻奈の\n曲をカバーすることにファンの期待が高まっている」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "the legendary idol Nagase Mana's song\nhas raised fans' expectations.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.7333788395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "……何も問題ないと思うが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I don't see any problem with that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.8395197344,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "問題はこの後です！\n「疑問なのは、サニピと月ストが合同で歌うことだ」",
      "translations": {
